quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,By the fig and the olive
  95,2,And Mount Sinai
  95,3,And this safe land
  95,4,We created man in the best design
  95,5,Then reduced him to the lowest of the low
  95,6,Except those who believe and do righteous deeds; for them is a reward without end
  95,7,So why do you still reject the religion
  95,8,Is God not the Wisest of the wise